{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know a lot of people are judgmental about what happened, because they feel that if a woman wants out of a marriage with three children, especially three daughters, there is something wrong with her, you see?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I suppose if you look-- if you were to ask some of my friends, they would say that it was her fault, and everything-- and I was the saint.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Be that as it may, I don't-- I don't believe that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was a good husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I was a good child, I was a good husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she married for, for the wrong reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was a strong enough personality to decide that she really didn't want this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She really-- this is not the sort of life she wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't think she was ready to take on the responsibilities of marriage and three children, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She wanted a different life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She wanted to be an actress, and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I think-- and in lots of ways I think that-- well, if people watch this tape-- it's the truth, anyway, what difference does it make?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think she was pushed by her-- by her mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which is not unusual for, you know, for a Jewish mother to want her daughter to marry a Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it's epitome of, of success, isn't it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you're 20-- and I think back now, I see my own children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, at the age of 20, not my daughters would not know who to marry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if they came along with a guy who was Jewish, who was 32, was a doctor, I'd throw up my hands in horror and say, this is disgusting, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You raised your daughters?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
